strings: <voice_0x010012A6><se_high>The beautiful rose: Jessica! When will you be back? <:>)
<voice_0x010012A7><se_high>Accuracy: I will have to leave now
<voice_0x010012A8><se_high>Accuracy: We have not yet been contacted to find out who is responsible for Alistair's death...sorry...
<voice_0x010012AA><se_high>The beautiful rose: ... don't worry, do what you want.
<voice_0x010012AB><se_high>The beautiful rose: I will definitely come back when everything is ok.
<voice_0x010012AC><se_high>The beautiful rose: <Cap><hero> I want to give you something.
<voice_0x010012AF><se_high>The beautiful rose: Alistair's shield. Alistair's son armor. Thank you for accepting. It is convenient when you are sure to climb.
<voice_0x010012B0><se_high>The beautiful rose: I do not like the powder that I want to use
<voice_0x010012B2><se_high>The beautiful rose: This is exactly what Jessica needs!
